data.description: Table Rock Lake build site in the heart of beautiful Kimberling City! With the housing inventory as low as ever why not stop the endless hunt and build that dream home instead! Now offering this .33 acre build site in sought after Kimberling Hills subdivision with city water, sewer, electric, high-speed internet, and peaceful wooded views with potential for views of crystal clear Table Rock Lake with a little clearing (neighboring homes boast bridge/lake views). Need a little more room to expand? Seller is also offering adjoining lots 3&5, approx 0.3-.4 acres each for addition $29,900.00 per lot. All less than 5 minutes to heart of lake loving Kimberling City with popular Port of Kimberling Marina, seasonal farmers markets, local boutiques/eateries, grocery store, post office, spas, and more! And less than 10 minutes to Reeds Spring Schools, and about 20 minutes to Branson with world class dining/entertainment, and even more adventure hiking/biking Mark Twain National Forest. Come live the lake life you have always dreamed at Longview Drive!
